title: BONUS: Antonio Brown to the Patriots! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Instant reaction to the big news. Dave thinks Antonio Brown is right up there with Mike Evans, but Adam isn't so sure. What does this do to Julian Edelman and Josh Gordon? Is Gordon in the Will Fuller range now? Any impact on James White or Sony Michel? And wow, Tom Brady could be great.
